  EffectDiscription_ENG: "[Main] 1 of your Digimon gains \uFF1CPiercing\uFF1E for
    the turn. (When this Digimon attacks and deletes an opponent's Digimon, it performs
    any security checks it normally would.) Then, if you have a Digimon in play with
    [Angoramon] in its name or digivolution cards, suspend 1 of your opponent's Digimon."
